    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/966043ccca98ccd6ce6da4ebd64470f6.avif?t=1721787151\" width=629 height=154 /></span><br>跳绳太乏味？《运动派对》让你的健身更有趣。这款体感游戏，以科技替代跳绳，让锻炼变得轻松愉快。它不仅好玩，还能全面锻炼你的身体。自从我加入，每天的健身都充满期待。试试吧，让《运动派对》带你体验健身新乐趣，一起体验健身新境界，让健康成为你的生活方式！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/346d209c3b1099fdde13ac355a33bba9.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/346d209c3b1099fdde13ac355a33bba9.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/346d209c3b1099fdde13ac355a33bba9.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/bd53bf45e57fd6abf8cdef0f7a1a205e.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/bd53bf45e57fd6abf8cdef0f7a1a205e.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/bd53bf45e57fd6abf8cdef0f7a1a205e.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/f1b223a94aef678d2203b2c334d416a8.avif?t=1721787151\" width=564 height=148 /></span><br>是否每次健身都感觉像是在完成任务？《运动派对》能让你找到健身的乐趣。这款体感健身游戏，用游戏的快感打破健身的沉闷，让你在不知不觉中提升体能，减轻身体负担。它不只是让你动起来，更是让你享受其中。你也应该来尝试，我确信你的身体会感谢你。别等了，让《运动派对》成为你的健身新伙伴，一起享受健康生活的每一刻！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/abab669528ca50fc456dc8f8532c53f3.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/abab669528ca50fc456dc8f8532c53f3.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/abab669528ca50fc456dc8f8532c53f3.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/03bd72b36a26933224e948a8918d063f.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/03bd72b36a26933224e948a8918d063f.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/03bd72b36a26933224e948a8918d063f.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/dc03ac171508dc88238a8b03c2917f13.avif?t=1721787151\" width=554 height=148 /></span><br>游戏精心设计了20个独特的健身关卡，每个关卡都有不同的健身动作和挑战目标。玩家需要在限定时间内完成指定动作，以获得更高的分数和奖励。随着关卡的推进，难度逐渐增加，考验玩家的协调性、速度和耐力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/eea5eab4311e4f7ebe18f4c7ad22c9fb.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/eea5eab4311e4f7ebe18f4c7ad22c9fb.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/eea5eab4311e4f7ebe18f4c7ad22c9fb.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/2f5b902374490e31f413c17d3775c912.avif?t=1721787151\" width=552 height=146 /></span><br>《运动派对》支持两名玩家在线对抗，您可以邀请好友一起加入健身挑战，相互比拼，共同进步。在线对抗模式不仅增加了游戏的互动性，还能激发玩家的竞技热情，让健身变得更加有趣和激烈。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/cface8a961f006c6e192f0a33ca86bfa.poster.avif?t=1721787151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/cface8a961f006c6e192f0a33ca86bfa.webm?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067960/extras/cface8a961f006c6e192f0a33ca86bfa.mp4?t=1721787151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
